    "name": "Ball Race Party",
    "steam_appid": 3202400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/8cf7db73137f421fcd0c37a53ec23855.poster.avif?t=1756127401\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/8cf7db73137f421fcd0c37a53ec23855.webm?t=1756127401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/8cf7db73137f421fcd0c37a53ec23855.mp4?t=1756127401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物理乐趣</strong>：体验真实物理效果，增加趣味挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞速与策略</strong>：完美结合运气与技巧的游戏玩法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样与激情</strong>：从具有挑战性的单人关卡到有趣的多人模式，总有适合你的内容！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来加入 <strong>Ball Race Party</strong> 的世界吧！终点线在等着你！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>单人模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与时间赛跑！在这个模式中，你将面对越来越困难的赛道，测试你的速度与技巧。用最短时间完成关卡，登上全球排行榜榜首。反应迅速、策略得当，打破纪录！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/f20a97daf0ee3419700d31e82e06a85d.poster.avif?t=1756127401\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/f20a97daf0ee3419700d31e82e06a85d.webm?t=1756127401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/f20a97daf0ee3419700d31e82e06a85d.mp4?t=1756127401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多人模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ball Race Party</strong> 提供两种令人兴奋的多人模式：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1. 挑战模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展现你的技能！在这个模式中，你需要与其他玩家竞争，用最快速度完成一条充满挑战的赛道。克服障碍，采取策略，甩开对手。记住，不仅需要速度，还需要战术！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2. 幸运模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不受你控制！你选择的球完全按照自己的轨迹移动，你只能紧张地观看。相信运气，期待你的球比对手的球更早到达终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/5a5cf6c5df2b7d8f5ce371999061e69d.poster.avif?t=1756127401\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/5a5cf6c5df2b7d8f5ce371999061e69d.webm?t=1756127401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/5a5cf6c5df2b7d8f5ce371999061e69d.mp4?t=1756127401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特殊技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在比赛中使用这些有趣的技能阻碍对手，获得优势：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>臭屁</strong>：制造一个短暂的障碍，阻止后面的对手。时机掌握很关键！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>炸弹</strong>：用强大的爆炸将对手从赛道上击飞。策略性地使用它，抢占领先位置。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
